            | Highlights include a multi-part
            em Production-Ready
            |  series (memory dump tooling, structured logging,
            | performance metrics, testing strategy) and hands-on debugging write-ups.
            | Cadence is uneven — a daughter recently arrived who has discovered that closing a laptop lid is the most effective scheduling mechanism available to her.

        // Interests
        .section
